videos.description: Kansas guard Devon Dotson drives towards the basket and flips in a layup with his left hand.

videos.headline: Kansas' Dotson flies in to make tough layup

videos.description: Oklahoma guard Jamal Bieniemy lobs the ball up to forward Kur Kuath, who finishes with a two-handed dunk.

videos.description: Kansas guard Marcus Garrett gets a steal that turns into a Devon Dotson layup. On Oklahoma's next possession, Garrett steals the ball again and drives in for his own layup.

videos.description: Oklahoma's Austin Reaves tries to drive in for a layup, but Kansas' Udoka Azubuike jumps high to swat the shot away.
